title: Live from Chicago!
description: It's a Chicago-towne reunion show with all comedians Pete started with back in the ol' windy city (no one calls it that)! some familiar faces ("fam faces") and some newbie chewbies ("newbie chewbies") for all weirdos, Chicagoans and not, to enjoy. T.J. Miller! Hannibal Buress! Matt Braunger! Sean Flannery! Robert Buscemi! And a sharpshooting CJ Sullivan! SO PLEASE ENJOY YOU WEIRDOS!!
